               <scopecontent id="aspace_d58d2a48728b71a6aa7d53877069eba8">
                  <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
                  <p>Autograph manuscript. Folios 1, 23, and 60, with about 10 others at end of manuscript (probably blank), have been cut out. Many leaves are written on both sides. FitzGerald's autograph pasted on fly-leaf. Accompanied by TLS from W. R. Browne to Thomas B. Mosher, TLS from Ralph A. Beals to Mr. Otis Bradley, and 2 periodical articles, all concerning the manuscript.</p>
